  "original_title": "Sri Lanka President flees to Maldives",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka President flees to Maldives",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka President Gotabaya Rajapaksa had fled to the Maldives in a military aircraft, reports said as his resignation is expected later in the day amid the worst currency crisis in the history of the island\u2019s intermediate regime central bank.",
        "Sri Lanka\u2019s Derana Television quoted Air Force Spokesman Group Dushan Wijesinghe as saying that on a of the existing government request President Rajapaksa, his wife and two body guards had left the country in an Air Force aircraft.",
        "The French News Agency reported that President Rajapaksa had left in a Antonov 32 aircraft to the Maldives.",
        "Sri Lanka President Rajapaksa is expected to give his resignation today, according to an earlier statement by the speaker."
      ],
